00:00:05.450 --> 00:00:10.410
TV is a new game.  It's about finding the content at the time you want to watch it,

00:00:10.410 --> 00:00:13.679
on whatever screen you want to watch it,

00:00:13.679 --> 00:00:18.039
and I think this is a really the challenge
to find a user experience that

00:00:18.039 --> 00:00:23.149
attracts people to buy the service and
that's why it's important to conduct

00:00:23.149 --> 00:00:26.980
consumer research and that's what we
have ConsumerLabs,

00:00:26.980 --> 00:00:33.050
to find out what customers all over the world
are asking for.

00:00:33.050 --> 00:00:37.600
We use the consumer knowledge in order
to base Ericsson's products and services

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:40.510
